{"tid":712227,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"史上頭一遭！為吃狗肉殺狗 南韓法院判有罪","createTime":"2018-06-22T02:51:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-25T03:50:42.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"72fd6c62a34546cfaa63cb33694331e457eaa3dd","tid":712227,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T02:51:30.000Z","msg":"吃狗肉影響南韓國際形象，但始終沒有明文禁止。南韓富川市法院月前判決為吃狗肉而屠宰狗屬非法行為，判決細節最近才公布，動保團體對此表示歡迎，希望為全面禁止吃狗肉鋪路。<br />\n<br />\n南韓法令並未禁止吃狗肉，只有動保法禁止狗場及餐廳以殘忍方法殺害狗兒。動保團體Care去年投訴富川一名狗場老闆，指控他「沒有適當原因便殺害狗兒」，及違反建築及衛生條例。<br />\n<br />\n法新社廿一日報導，南韓法院在今年四月判決狗場老闆罪名成立，罰款三百萬韓元（約八萬台幣），因被告放棄上訴而定讞。Care的代表律師金京垠形容判決非常有意義，是首次判決為了吃狗肉而殺狗是違法。<br />\n<br />\n狗場老闆對判決相當不滿，業者代表曹桓魯認為政府應將吃狗肉合法化，將肉食狗隻與寵物狗分開，否則將抗爭到底，他並反問：「牛、豬、雞、鴨都能飼養為消費肉品，狗為何不行？」<br />\n<br />\n狗肉在南韓被視為夏季補品，去年一項民調發現百分之七十的南韓人不吃狗肉，但是認為應該禁食狗肉的比率只有百分之四十。<br />\n<br />\nCare的總幹事朴韶妍指出，對於吃狗肉的大眾論述正逐漸轉向禁止，該團體將充分運用此一判決，舉報全國其他狗場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E9%A0%AD-%E9%81%AD-%E7%82%BA%E5%90%83%E7%8B%97%E8%82%89%E6%AE%BA%E7%8B%97-%E5%8D%97%E9%9F%93%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2%E5%88%A4%E6%9C%89%E7%BD%AA-230811057.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%258F%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E9%25A0%25AD-%25E9%2581%25AD-%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%2590%2583%25E7%258B%2597%25E8%2582%2589%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E7%258B%2597-%25E5%258D%2597%25E9%259F%2593%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2599%25A2%25E5%2588%25A4%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25BD%25AA-230811057.html&d=RpIL%2BEEzppGsfSiXGw8IIGowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=c43f9b42\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E9%A0%AD-%E9%81%AD-%E7%82%BA%E5%90%83%E7%8B%97%E8%82%89%E6%AE%BA%E7%8B%97-%E5%8D%97%E9%9F%93%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2%E5%88%A4%E6%9C%89%E7%BD%AA-230811057.html</a><br />\n<br />\n泡菜崛起<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/south_korea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95817b2cbf68b5a2a34d45d07f4622dbba974305","tid":712227,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T03:44:17.000Z","msg":"連登狗肉撚全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1583ea0c7ea2f2ebe38952a348c8b1a96db1fe71","tid":712227,"uid":41524,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T03:45:58.000Z","msg":"雜種狗學人談論仁義道德"},{"pid":"9e1fb24b79e89bcae0daff83042ba08f8ff2881f","tid":712227,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T04:24:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a866e610f95da312a5f397d32d8b86fa960535d","tid":712227,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T04:31:31.000Z","msg":"又世界大戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40e77b1e7b8c476a88098e6e7d188248ce6aa012","tid":712227,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T04:33:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea0269fc76d8050999fe73dc5dbf45836a8bf79a","tid":712227,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T03:50:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}